#- §lBook the First:§0
§0§oin which I learned how to pronounce "wj"§0
§0
§0As I neared my journey's end§0
§0A slapping sounded 'round the bend.§0
§0"How strange" I mused, for this was not§0
§0A noise mine ears before had caught.§0
§0"Hail" said I, "Who doth go there?"
#- The slapping sound yet filled the air.§0
§b█████████████████§f██§b█████████§f█████§b█████████████████§2▟█▖ §b███████§0
