#- So now for all the curious§0
§0who see uwuj and think "what's this?"§0
§0It doesn't matter which you say:§0
§0be it wj or wj.§0
§0Some will tell you they won't budge,§0
§0insisting it's wj or wj.§0
§0In truth, it's just a way to spread§0
§0the strange condition to your head
#- For on page 8 I gave my name,§0
§0but now you see it's not the same. §0
§0And so I end this Book the First,§0
§0and tell you how you have been cursed! §0
